# signalos brain

Persistent AI memory index. Pure-Python BM25, no runtime deps.

## When to use
- Store gate artifacts after signing: `signalos brain put "$(cat PLAN.md)" --source PLAN.md --gate G2 --wave 09 --type artifact`
- Retrieve context before a design session: `signalos brain search "design decision" --top 5`
- Audit what was ingested: `signalos brain list --wave 09`
- Clean up stale entries: `signalos brain prune brain-007`

## Key behaviours
- Index lives at `.signalos/brain/index.jsonl` (append-only)
- Prune = tombstone record, never destructive
- `upgrade --embeddings` requires `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`; falls back to BM25 silently
- C15 wiring-guard: index present → `brain-auto-ingest.sh` must exist
